		<div id="comment_body_64612895"><p>3 of the 4 methods definitely allow that, and the 4th depends on how aggressive the slowly reduce speed is.</p><p>It'd be interesting to see how much travel time they actually add in a remote emergency situation though.</p></div>
	</div>

